	(164,'_transient_dash_de3249c4736ad3bd2cd29147c4a0d43e','<h4>最热门的</h4>\n<h5><a href=\'http://wordpress.org/plugins/wordfence/\'>Wordfence Security</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=wordfence&amp;_wpnonce=f0d5973b3e&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Wordfence Security\'>安装</a>)</span>\n<p>Wordfence Security is a free enterprise class security and performance plugin that makes your site up to 50 times faster and more secure.</p>\n<h4>最新插件</h4>\n<h5><a href=\'https://wordpress.org/plugins/remove-css-link-ids/\'>Remove CSS link IDs</a></h5>&nbsp;<span>(<a href=\'plugin-install.php?tab=plugin-information&amp;plugin=remove-css-link-ids&amp;_wpnonce=dead569d45&amp;TB_iframe=true&amp;width=600&amp;height=800\' class=\'thickbox\' title=\'Remove CSS link IDs\'>安装</a>)</span>\n<p>WP plugin that removes the ID attributes from the  tags for the CSS files. Used mostly together with mod_pagespeed.</p>\n','no'),
